<title>INDIA: India Infosys to meet for bonus, results.</title>
<headline>India Infosys to meet for bonus, results.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-04-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Leading software maker Infosys Technologies said on Friday its board of directors would meet on April 8 to finalise results for 1996/97 (April-March) and to discuss a bonus issue of shares.</p>
<p>-- Bombay newsroom +91-22-265 9000</p>
